Drawing. Illustrating. Sharing my creativity through pictures. Creating worlds and characters for stories and role playing games. After comparing a lot of yays and nays and a good opportunity to get everything going I started developing deeper knowledge and drawing skills. In October 2014 I decided to go freelance and focus on concept art and character design.

[http://www.boldtsketches.de/](http://www.boldtsketches.de/)
